article.headline: Southern U. 67, Alcorn St. 61
article.story: LORMAN, Miss., La. (AP) -- Chris Davis had 18 points and Joseph Jack 15 to lead Southern in a 67-61 victory over Alcorn State on Saturday. Southern (9-18, 7-9 SWAC) led 32-31 at halftime. Anthony Ford had 12 points for Alcorn (6-23, 5-11); Alex Owumi, Adrian Oliver and Troy Jackson had 11 each. Owumi also had 10 rebounds.
